profile:
TimberWolf Industries is Canada's Premier Tiny House Builders and Muskoka's complete cottage services provider.

Located in the heart of the Muskoka's TimberWolf Industries builds some of the best Tiny Houses as well as provides a complete line of cottage services. From snow removal and ice management services to construction and renovation services, You can count on TimberWolf Industries to surpass your expectations. 

Please feel free to visit our website at www.timberwolfindustries.ca for further information.
